Package: SocialGrowthIndex
Type: Project
Title: Social Growth Index for Italian Municipalities
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Research", "Team", email = "research@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A composite measure of socioeconomic resilience for Italian municipalities (2010-2022).
    Integrates FRK-based spatial downscaling of GDP with Copeland ranking over GDP density,
    GDP per capita, and population density. Includes code and pipelines for reproducible analysis.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
